# Vue template — test hooks (`data-test-*`)

UI test locator attributes. Pairs with [playwright-tests.mdc](playwright-tests.mdc) (`selectorList`, locators in `*.playwright.*.ts`; rare full selector strings for portaled nodes without hooks, e.g. `'[role="tooltip"]'`).

## Do not use bare `data-test`

- **Never** `data-test="..."` on production templates. Use **`data-test-locator="..."`** (or `:data-test-locator`) — primary stable id; Playwright/Vitest: `[data-test-locator="..."]`.
- Extra hyphenated attributes only when tests need more semantics (below).

## Primary locator

- **`data-test-locator`** — stable string per node (often `componentName-role-suffix`, e.g. `dialogAppSettings-title`, `globalWindowButtons-button-minimize`). Tests: `selectorList` + `appWindow.locator(\`[data-test-locator="${selectorList.someKey}"]\`)`.

## Other `data-test-*` hooks in this repo

- **`data-test-setting-id`**, **`data-test-tags`**, **`data-test-tooltip-text`** — App settings rows, help icons ([DialogAppSettings.vue](src/components/dialogs/DialogAppSettings/DialogAppSettings.vue)).
- Menu bar: **`data-test-menu-test`**, **`data-test-menu-any`** on [AppControlMenus.vue](src/components/globals/AppControlMenus/AppControlMenus.vue) ([AppControlMenus.playwright.test.ts](src/components/globals/AppControlMenus/_tests/AppControlMenus.playwright.test.ts)); Playwright: `[data-test-menu-test="..."]` / `[data-test-menu-any="..."]`.
- Metadata / flags via attributes or `dataset`: **`data-test-image`**, **`data-test-is-random`**, **`data-test-layout-width`**, **`data-test-layout-height`** ([FantasiaMascotImage.vue](src/components/elements/FantasiaMascotImage/FantasiaMascotImage.vue)); same layout keys on **[SocialContactSingleButton](src/components/elements/SocialContactSingleButton/SocialContactSingleButton.vue)** **q-img** and splash **SVG** in **[index.html](index.html)**; **`data-test-error-card-width`**, **`data-test-locator="errorCard-title"`**, **`data-test-locator="errorCard-details"`** on **[ErrorCard](src/components/elements/ErrorCard/ErrorCard.vue)** (max-width cap in CSS px + title/body). **`data-test-button-number`** ([SocialContactButtons.vue](src/components/other/SocialContactButtons/SocialContactButtons.vue)), **`data-test-has-proper-data-input`** ([AppControlSingleMenu.vue](src/components/globals/AppControlSingleMenu/AppControlSingleMenu.vue)).

## Naming

- Value: **lowerCamelCase block** + hyphen segments, e.g. `globalWindowButtons-button-minimize`, `dialogMarkdownDocument-markdown-wrapper`.
- Child components: shorter/compound names consistent with subtree (e.g. `socialContactSingleButton-image`).
- **Stay consistent** with component + existing `selectorList` in `_tests/*.playwright.test.ts`.

## Workflow

1. Add/update template hooks (`data-test-locator` + extra `data-test-*` as needed).
2. Update Playwright `selectorList` + tests ([playwright-tests.mdc](playwright-tests.mdc)); Vitest/Storybook same attribute names.
3. Rebuild before Playwright ([README.md](README.md)).

## Not in this rule

- BEM classes → [vue-bem-scss.mdc](vue-bem-scss.mdc).
- Quasar / Composition API / script extraction → [vue-quasar.mdc](vue-quasar.mdc).
